Informational Program Guide

   Questions from federal agencies about the statutory informational
   program requirement and about obtaining additional copies of the OSC
   informational program guide for federal agencies on diskette (one per
   agency request) should be directed to:

   Ms. Karen Dalheim, Attorney
   U.S. Office of Special Counsel
   1730 M Street, N.W., Suite 201
   Washington, D.C. 20036-4505
   Tel: (202) 653-9485
   Fax: (202) 653-5161
     __________________________________________________________________

Annual Reports

   Copies of OSC annual reports may be obtained, subject to availability,
   by writing or contacting:

   Director, Congressional and Public Affairs
   U.S. Office of Special Counsel
   1730 M Street, N.W., Suite 201
   Washington, D.C. 20036-4505
   Tel: (202) 653-5163
   Fax: (202) 653-5161

   Copies of annual reports after FY 1996 are available on this web site
   (see Forms and Publications)
     __________________________________________________________________

